    • readStaffsFromFile

      private static void readStaffsFromFile()
      Read from CAMSApp.STAFF_FILE_PATH to generate the staff arrayList.

      This methods generates the default Staff object, without any created camps under him. Use readCampsFromFile() to restore the created camps.

    • readCampsFromFile

      private static void readCampsFromFile()
      Read from camps_list.csv to generate the camp arrayList, and restores the created camps in staff.

      This method generates the default Camp object, without any participants, withdrawn participants, enquires, and suggestions under it. Use readStudentsFromFile(), readEnquiriesFromFile(), readSuggestionsFromFile() to restore them.

    • readStudentsFromFile
